	</p>
	
	
	<div class="jac-add-button"><a class="jac-links" style="background: url('http://www.chinacno.org/components/com_jacomment/asset/images/comment.png') no-repeat left center; padding-left: 16px;" href="comments/artists/3-让%2590%2590永%2581%2592%259A%2584%258C走" title="发表评论">发表评论</a>
							
		
					
		<span class="jac-count-comment">(2)</span></div>	
