<div class="item">

		<div class="icon email"><a href="component/mailto/index.html?tmpl=component&amp;template=yoo_studio&amp;link=0aab0cd42ebfdd8d37e508e813a23d150298b77d" title="Email" onclick="window.open(this.href,'win2','width=400,height=350,menubar=yes,resizable=yes'); return false;"><img src="http://www.chinacno.org/media/system/images/emailButton.png" alt="Email"  /></a></div>
	
		<div class="icon print"><a href="comments/music/396-%2593%2581读%2580%258A%2589%258C%258C%2580%258B?tmpl=component&amp;print=1&amp;layout=default&amp;page=" title="打印" onclick="window.open(this.href,'win2','status=no,toolbar=no,scrollbars=yes,titlebar=no,menubar=no,resizable=yes,width=640,height=480,directories=no,location=no'); return false;" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.chinacno.org/media/system/images/printButton.png" alt="打印"  /></a></div>
	
		<h1 class="title">

					<a href="comments/music/396-%2593%2581读%2580%258A%2589%258C%258C%2580%258B" title="品读《艳歌行》">品读《艳歌行》</a>
		
	</h1>
	
		<p class="meta">

		编辑：肖文礼  2013年3月07日 14:01. 发表于 <a href="comments/music.1">乐评</a>	
	
	</p>
	
	
	<div class="content"><p>
	作者：肖文礼</p>
<p>
	岁末甫至，年味儿愈浓，人们以一种节庆的、仪式的方式迎接新年。于是，从拥堵的交通中、长龙般的购票队伍旁、年货堆砌的大型超市里，可以体察一座城市的忙碌和人们心理上的&ldquo;非日常&rdquo;。此时，公共场所出现的高频词莫过于&ldquo;迎新春&rdquo;、&ldquo;贺新年&rdquo;诸如此类，各大剧场、音乐厅以&ldquo;辞旧迎新&rdquo;冠名的音乐会纷至踏来，其曲目多为表现热闹场面与喜庆氛围的&ldquo;宏大叙事&rdquo;，彰显出大家伙迎接新年的欢快心情与隆重心态。</p>
</div>


		<p class="links">
	
		
		<a href="comments/music/396-%2593%2581读%2580%258A%2589%258C%258C%2580%258B" title="品读《艳歌行》">
			阅读全文		</a>
		
	</p>
	
	
